{"tid":2283144,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《天穗之咲稻姬》Steam 定價比台灣高   中國玩家鬧爆日本遊戲商","createTime":"2020-11-12T10:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T15:06:42.000Z","uid":105678,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"965ca9d55a32914b873c67f0fa128ec88361a10c","tid":2283144,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1112-3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F1112-3a.jpg&h=d19b7bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲平台 Steam 一直對中國玩家相當友善，除了讓玩家接觸到更多海外開發商的遊戲，更重要是定價往往比其他國家優惠。一款在 Steam 上架的遊戲《天穗之咲稻姬》最近卻引發爭議，引起了很多中國玩家不滿，群起在論壇表達對日本開發商的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n《天穗之咲稻姬》是一款 RPG 類遊戲，女主角一邊種田耕作，一邊打倒日本傳統的妖魔鬼怪。遊戲上架 Steam 後一直相安無事，直到有中國網民在遊戲論壇表示《天穗之咲稻姬》的中國售價 350 人民幣，比起台灣、香港和日本的定價都要貴，就引發一直習慣便宜的中國玩家不滿。<br />\n<br />\n有中國玩家留言「小日本日常操作，就是噁心人」、「Steam 建議中國為低價區，但小日本不領情」、「Switch 版也才 260 元，這是宰豬吧，高貴日本惹不起」、「是不是都覺得中國是人傻錢多？」、「原本很有興趣的，明顯就是把我們當豬宰 」和「這定價搞錯了吧，你們是不是看成HKD了？」。不過 Steam 給予遊戲發行商上架和定價的自由，而定價亦反映他們對不同市場的想法，可能是他們認為中國玩家的消費能力已經超越台灣和香港，直逼售價最高的瑞士。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：ettoday"},{"pid":"287ee6c124658f4cf0e203ed23ccfe781eafd3c7","tid":2283144,"uid":286897,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:55:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e485e04c723dcfe568233f5c8841f68a35960be6","tid":2283144,"uid":62318,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:01:04.000Z","msg":"反正定低定高都會比小粉紅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正佢地話唔話都會照買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e19ed95cdf6cafb0fd375ce2c4871e4270de012","tid":2283144,"uid":145277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:06:52.000Z","msg":"咁steam咪日日歧視香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咩logic"},{"pid":"ac759d60f52737f9bb5f4ac90e87f1e8f374572c","tid":2283144,"uid":44160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:13:07.000Z","msg":"大陸狗同黑人一撚樣麻鳩煩"},{"pid":"4253855e5a82f8802ac269b97f1279ecb9b9ae88","tid":2283144,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:15:34.000Z","msg":"都冇諗住買架啦班垃圾，等玩翻版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ded4629310e196cf2f8452be60f1d89636ede4f","tid":2283144,"uid":236364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:19:51.000Z","msg":"不爽不要玩，親<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b911bb93071148c559cdfbd446fe2076bb1296c0","tid":2283144,"uid":171134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:28:36.000Z","msg":"點撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又成撚日話中國好撚有錢<br />\n不嬲發達地方賣高啲㗎啦<br />\n台灣咁撚窮唔賣平啲台仔點買得起"},{"pid":"8c97080dcb97ae44c8d69f6e413e0c0b31b7ad2e","tid":2283144,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:32:49.000Z","msg":"咁有骨氣就唔好買，成日真香真香<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4e7c1e7fd823c00a25a26439cbe6c30c454f58","tid":2283144,"uid":266010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:34:14.000Z","msg":"睇睇有冇先 買"},{"pid":"79e5b3b0fb3a4d95ea9aa88b9809e6b4b76c971b","tid":2283144,"uid":48149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:36:31.000Z","msg":"强大了 蛾的蝈"},{"pid":"76eb5605e0044371519ae2ca43468fd26a2722d0","tid":2283144,"uid":77164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:37:45.000Z","msg":"iPhone都係"},{"pid":"2c03de512d9f1e710991a834b2c738b396e7b8d5","tid":2283144,"uid":317378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c97080dcb97ae44c8d69f6e413e0c0b31b7ad2e","tid":2283144,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:32:49.000Z","msg":"咁有骨氣就唔好買，成日真香真香<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /